+ * model as the NSMenu bar), so this file may stay nearly empty. It exists
+ * as W1's seam for any NSApplication/NSMenu-level work that GTK cannot
+ * express (e.g. the application menu's "About"/"Services" items) — and now
+ * the dev-run Dock icon (see nautilus_macos_menu_init).
